{"tid":989750,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人好掛住走左既親人","createTime":"2019-01-21T05:52:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-26T10:27:16.000Z","uid":51981,"like":49,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"d398cb12e52a25a0ae7f6427f8841f984ea27b91","tid":989750,"uid":51981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T05:52:36.000Z","msg":"近排好多野做好大壓力<br />\n突然醒起今年8月係嫲嫲走左十年既日子<br />\n雖然我知道死亡對佢係一種解脫<br />\n但係一諗我細個既時候佢好健康 會用震聾人耳仔聲線講野 同兩三啖就ko一個格仔餅<br />\n去到我讀小學 佢跌親 隻腳魚左三個月都未好返 明明好想食格仔餅但只係食到一啖<br />\n到最後幾個月佢直頭講唔到野食唔到野行唔到<br />\n我真係好掛住你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我有好多野想同你講 我應該要學你講既語言而唔係埋怨你好重口音<br />\n你知唔知我讀呢個major都係因為你<br />\n我好想再聞到你陣老人除<br />\n點解你要走 <br />\n點解你唔可以留多幾年<br />\n我好掛住你"},{"pid":"d3175eebc9411be9d1df5e2cd5b5954973d70b12","tid":989750,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T05:54:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25fcad8ef7e30db0e85bd31fd11e5ef2358c0e2f","tid":989750,"uid":202496,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T05:55:29.000Z","msg":"老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cbc21660100a1f5b59a6821c5ed30590e3474ac","tid":989750,"uid":31522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T05:55:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"83cd52ac5c2f9f65ca3cc3df1cae1da61d0a6985","tid":989750,"uid":106482,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T05:57:33.000Z","msg":"唉<br />\n我都好怕有呢一日<br />\n我婆婆都八十幾歲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n已經不斷提自己要有心理預備"},{"pid":"d99b32378fbbbf1b1ab0352675d46c67e04fc15b","tid":989750,"uid":75425,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T06:01:39.000Z","msg":"記得前幾年係冬至前個幾日，婆婆仲好開心叫我地冬至個日記得黎佢屋企食飯，我仲大大聲話一定到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點知去到冬至個日就係婆婆過生個日。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到呢刻我仲忘記唔到飛的由屯門趕出去，但佢最後一面都見唔到嘅個個心情。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n婆婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc18a4012fd97d0673aa27e755749b6ac8ba6da1","tid":989750,"uid":9941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T06:02:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇完呢個post"},{"pid":"705bf63b7d1118ef29fd71c3ad8f4dd5de6d8108","tid":989750,"uid":48276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T06:03:47.000Z","msg":"爺爺<br />\n我係日本買左個好似米通既零食啊<br />\n岩曬你口味<br />\n可惜你唔係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6590e9cf139722c9ef15cbe196de6389b41bd4d5","tid":989750,"uid":34777,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T06:07:25.000Z","msg":"好掛住婆婆你啲蘿蔔糕呀<br />\n你依家過得好嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98514c3a35dc58456d34cd6afd3ec3f2bbd34e2c","tid":989750,"uid":34777,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T06:08:51.000Z","msg":"因為我好驚失去<br />\n所以捉得好緊<br />\n我好驚失去我媽咪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n儘量日日抽時間番去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n媽咪I love U<br />\n希望你可以陪我一世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9cb5cca037a0a2c2cfc6ad0f648244e79d6eec1","tid":989750,"uid":54359,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T06:12:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcc21647cfc1ee1f58