ke":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T12:51:55.000Z","msg":"嫲嫲好似1年定2年前走, 9x歲<br />\n靈堂陪訓一晚, 但太凍, 半夜上返車訓<br />\n第2日belibala打晒band做儀式/法事~<br />\n跟住我負責抱遺照一行幾十人去火葬場<br />\n燒完成大陣椒鹽瀨尿蝦味... 大陸興唔燒到咁盡咁灰, 所以會見到頭骨外形etc...<br />\n仲有啲金屬支架剩返, (跌斷骨裝上去)<br />\n<br />\n從此以後, 永遠唔會再食 椒鹽瀨尿蝦, 本身都唔鐘意食海鮮<br />\n<br />\nbtw, 可能份人冷血, 無乜點傷心/喊, 或者一早已經睇開左生老病死<br />\nps. 細個嫲嫲好錫我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20a969b1c387a84ba94ffe164be41ecf0dedac21","tid":989750,"uid":17904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"816a2d5519466fb3f3be528fa33f57276d23e227","tid":989750,"uid":18844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T12:51:55.000Z","msg":"嫲嫲好似1年定2年前走, 9x歲<br />\n靈堂陪訓一晚, 但太凍, 半夜上返車訓<br />\n第2日belibala打晒band做儀式/法事~<br />\n跟住我負責抱遺照一行幾十人去火葬場<br />\n燒完成大陣椒鹽瀨尿蝦味... 大陸興唔燒到咁盡咁灰, 所以會見到頭骨外形etc...<br />\n仲有啲金屬支架剩返, (跌斷骨裝上去)<br />\n<br />\n從此以後, 永遠唔會再食 椒鹽瀨尿蝦, 本身都唔鐘意食海鮮<br />\n<br />\nbtw, 可能份人冷血, 無乜點傷心/喊, 或者一早已經睇開左生老病死<br />\nps. 細個嫲嫲好錫我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T12:54:28.000Z","msg":"傷心同喊係兩回事喎，唔喊都無問題，唔傷心就...."},{"pid":"c4be1cfad2776e5666aaf1cd94d2f123d46be9da","tid":989750,"uid":219650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T12:55:52.000Z","msg":"哼，我諗我死左都唔知有冇人掛住我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aec3e985ab90acb55ad8a07e5d22d4f104757330","tid":989750,"uid":126561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T13:14:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GuqY5OViunk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DGuqY5OViunk&d=mfnejbsFhuLinHjNFaGmHG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=cb1ac72d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GuqY5OViunk</a><br />\n<br />\n最近睇完呢首mv<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再望返呢個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n身邊冇咩人走 就算走左既我都對佢地冇咩感覺<br />\n但我最驚係老豆老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都開始老<br />\n但自己岩岩fg出黎仲要咁快有回報可以報到佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3417383be756c67cd635a6b5c692dfd27be978a","tid":989750,"uid":39234,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T13:31:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}